name: Genshin NFT
description: GENSHIN is not a meme coin. IT’S the Metaverse. A new cryptocurrency birthed by fans & members of the Shiba Inu community. Genshin NFT is named after Elon Musk’s very own Shiba Inu. GENSHIN is working on three flagship utility projects: an NFT gaming metaverse known as GENSHIN, an NFT and merchandise marketplace known as GenshinSWAP, an NFT IDO marketplace known as GenshinIDO.
